'''itri''' ([[Asget]]: '''itran''') d [[tafekka tagnnawt]] n [[Plasma (tasengama)|plasma]], Meqqer, [[Asfijjej|yetfejjij]], yettwaṭṭef s tmentilt n [[taldayt|teldayt]] dɣa asfijjej-is yttekkes-it-id seg [[tafasa taɣisant|tfasa taɣisant]] i d-ittlalen deg-s, Anda [[abelkim|ibelkimen]] n [[Hidṛujin|uhidṛujin]] ttenṭaṭen gugar-asen ayen i d-igellun s [[aferdis akruran|iferdisen]] iẓẓayen ugar n uhidṛujin am [[Hilium|uhilium]] d [[Litium|ulitium]] d kra n iferdisen yefsusen am [[Uzzal|wuzzal]], Tasedmirt-a tasengamt tettusemma s [[azday aɣisan|wezday aɣisan]]

Itri yudsen (iqerben) yakk ɣer [[tagnit|tegnit]] d [[tafukt]], Acku d nettat i d aɣbalu n tfasa d tafat akken daɣen id tettaweṭ tfasa-ines ɣer [[itrikli|yimtiwgen]] n iṭen i d-tgin [[udud anafuk]], Kra n yetran d wid id ittbinen deg [[iṭ|yiṭ]] mi ara ad iba (ad iɣab) ayen iten-itteffren am [[asigna|usigna]] neɣ [[tafat]]<br/>
Tigrawin n yetran i d-ismgrawen deg yiwet n tarebbut isem-it-sent [[tazdemt]]
